# ⚠️ WARNING: This file is IGNORED in production.
# The site is deployed to GitHub Pages (see deploy-frontend-pages.sh), and
# GitHub Pages does NOT support `_headers` (that is a Cloudflare Pages / Netlify
# feature). Verified: live HSTS max-age=15552000 != the 31536000 declared below,
# and CSP / X-Frame-Options / Referrer-Policy are absent on the live site.
#
# Security headers MUST be applied at the Cloudflare edge instead.
# See: cloudflare/security-headers/README.md
# This file is kept only as the source-of-truth CSP draft for that config.

/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'sha256-EoEMHvabwGac6i7V+r9JW1TAGLf+DxjsSMD/zQ7L+bI=' 'unsafe-eval' https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com https://cdn.jsdelivr.net https://*.nine-security.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com https://cdn.jsdelivr.net; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com; img-src 'self' data: https://nine-security.com; connect-src 'self' https://*.nine-security.com https://*.workers.dev;
